reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater fits true to size with a perfect length, and appreciate its quality, comfort, and style, with one noting it can be dressed up or down. Customers praise its softness, texture, and warmth, particularly noting it's great for cold days.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality-true to size and so comfy!
items.body: The media could not be loaded. This is a medium weight material, true to size, however it’s styled as a bit oversized which I love above it. Super soft and comfy! Grab this! I’m ordering in other colors! Has a cute cuff at the wrists that are ribbed. It is also ribbed on the top half and smooth on the rest of the sweater. Watch my video for additional fun details. Great quality for the price. The color is a muted beautiful chocolate brown. Read more
items.author: sonjarenee2001

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute!
items.body: Cuter in person! Good quality and will be warm in the winter! Fit is great, it's just a bit oversized like the picture looks. I am a medium bought a medium when I usually go large on sweaters. Read more
items.author: Julie A

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but material kinda cheap
items.body: Love the color, material feels kinda cheap. I am interested to see how it does after first wash. Fit is good and slightly oversized. Read more
items.author: Carol H

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish, comfy and cute!
items.body: This sweater is amazing! Its the second sweater ive purchased from Dokotok and I LOVE it. Its soft to touch and not too heavyweight. i worse a thin tank top under it. The color was exactly as pictured! In the picture shared, ive stretched it to show how much room you have and the length . Im typically a XL, 5'9 but based on reviews I sized down to a large and i do not regret it! Read more
items.author: Richard and Amanda Smith

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Try it, you'll love it too!
items.body: LOVE! Normally a XL but I lost some weight and ordered the L. I'm happy with the fit overall, but would have liked to have longer sleeves. The puffiness of the sleeves is great! Just like the picture. Be warned, the type of weave and material this sweater is made of is prone to snagging. But has nothing to do with how it's made or fits. It's great material, soft, heavy but breathes. Order it in your true size :) Read more
items.author: Parker

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and comfortable
items.body: Nice sweater. True to size. Good quality and looks great Read more
items.author: Renee Surgener

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Unusual knit patterns in beautiful sweater.
items.body: Great sweater, beautiful combination of knits, rooming, sleeves particularly outstanding (full with narrow wrists). Great deal even with the increase in price with my second order (blue)l Read more
items.author: Dr. Pat

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight! Wear a layer under.
items.body: This sweater is soft and comfortable Very cute. I really like the style, especially the sleeves, I got lots of compliments on it. I will say it has a large knit on the sleeves and if wearing outdoors, wear something underneath because the cold air will go right through you! Also, it did have a couple of pulls in it, but i just pulled them back through and they were unnoticeable. Read more
items.author: Jennifer

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Sky Blue, Brown, Colorblock Brown, Apricot, Hot Pink, Black, Colorblock Blue, Orange, Colorblock Khaki, Dark Green, Red, Khaki, Pink, White. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
